    "title": "Connect the population: Access Now demands end to Iran’s continued internet blackout amid war",
    "link": "https://www.accessnow.org/press-release/iran-connect-the-population-statement/",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-11T11:45:17.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><div class=\"wp-block-columns has-light-gray-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-0d0c2599 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>Access Now condemns the ongoing near-total internet shutdown in Iran, which began on <a href=\"https://x.com/CloudflareRadar/status/2027709437981450502\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>February 28, 2026</strong></a>, and urgently calls on Iranian authorities to immediately restore full internet access and refrain from imposing further disruptions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Internet connectivity sharply dropped by more <a href=\"https://x.com/CloudflareRadar/status/2027709437981450502\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>than 98%</strong></a></p></div></div></body></html>",
    "creator": "Kassem Mnejja",
    "sourceTitle": "Access Now",
    "sheetCategory": "Human Rights + Democracy",
    "enforcedImage": null,
    "sourceDescription": "",
    "sourceLogo": "https://www.accessnow.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cropped-favicon-32x32.png",
    "lang": "en",
    "scope": "World",
    "isDarkLogo": false,
    "originalRssUrl": "https://www.accessnow.org/feed/"
  },
  {
    "title": "From cooperation to complicity: meet the companies powering the EU’s war on migrants",
    "link": "https://www.accessnow.org/companies-powering-eu-war-on-migrants/?pk_campaign=feed&pk_kwd=companies-powering-eu-war-on-migrants",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-11T06:00:00.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><p>Even as <a href=\"https://www.politico.eu/article/un-agency-iom-reports-unprecedented-death-toll-on-mediterranean-migration-route/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">people continue to die at Europe’s borders</a>, little is known about the private sector’s role in implementing increasingly <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q90UOO7oiRc?si=kmnpTTeF2luV_xPt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">draconian EU migration policies</a>. In fact, when it comes to migration, the cosy relationship between private companies and EU institutions is purposefully kept far from public view, escaping scrutiny and transparency. As </p></body></html>",
    "creator": "Caterina Rodelli",
    "sourceTitle": "Access Now",
    "sheetCategory": "Human Rights + Democracy",
    "enforcedImage": null,
    "sourceDescription": "",
    "sourceLogo": "https://www.accessnow.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cropped-favicon-32x32.png",
    "lang": "en",
    "scope": "World",
    "isDarkLogo": false,
    "originalRssUrl": "https://www.accessnow.org/feed/"
  },
  {
    "title": "Shadowy surveillance: Access Now maps the companies implementing the EU’s migration policies",
    "link": "https://www.accessnow.org/press-release/shadowy-surveillance-eu-migration-policies/",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-11T06:00:00.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><p>As the European Commission continues to fortify its migration policies and tighten border controls, <strong><a href=\"https://www.accessnow.org/companies-powering-eu-war-on-migrants/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Access Now’s latest research</a></strong> exposes the private sector companies building — and profiting from — the European Union’s (EU) extensive surveillance infrastructure, while influencing policy and practice. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The investigation focuses on how the private sector participates in industry pitch events hosted by three EU agencies responsible for implementing EU migration policies: <strong>eu-LISA,</strong> the agency responsible for managing the EU’s large-scale migration and policing databases; <strong>Frontex,</strong> which supports the managemen</p></body></html>",
    "creator": "Wajd",
    "sourceTitle": "Access Now",
    "sheetCategory": "Human Rights + Democracy",
    "enforcedImage": null,
    "sourceDescription": "",
    "sourceLogo": "https://www.accessnow.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/cropped-favicon-32x32.png",
