  {
    "title": "A call to EU legislators: protect rights and reject the call to delete transparency safeguard in AI Act",
    "link": "https://www.accessnow.org/press-release/a-call-to-eu-legislators-protect-transparency-safeguard-in-ai-act/",
    "pubDate": "2026-02-10T18:31:13.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><div class=\"wp-block-columns has-light-gray-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-0d0c2599 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>Dear Members of the European Parliament,<br>Dear Representatives of Member States of the European Union,<br>Dear Executive Vice-President Virkkunen,<br>Dear Commissioner McGrath,</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We, the undersigned organisations and individuals, <strong>urge you in the strongest possible terms to reject the deletion of the Article 49(2) transparency safeguard for high-risk AI systems</strong> that is proposed in the <strong></strong></p></div></div></body></html>",
